    "tab-collage-0": {
      "type": "tab-collage",
      "blocks": {
        "tab-collage-0-0": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image_position": "center center",
            "heading": "CRAFTED FOR THE SENSES",
            "description": "<p>You can see it in the soft lambskin leather, picked and stitched with exacting attention to detail. You can feel it in the precision-cut aluminium frame that's robust yet beautiful. Even the carry case tells the story. Timeless design, made to last for generations.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_size": "medium",
            "button_style_secondary": false,
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker"
          }
        },
        "tab-collage-0-1": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image_position": "center center",
            "heading": "LESS EFFORT. MORE EMOTION.",
            "description": "<p>Quick set up, intuitive user controls and Bluetooth 5.1 allow you to connect easily to the devices you already love. And if you want to make a few sounds of your own, four microphones keep your voice crystal clear on calls.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_size": "medium",
            "button_style_secondary": false,
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker"
          }
        },
        "tab-collage-0-3": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image_position": "center center",
            "heading": "STANDOUT ACCESSORIES",
            "description": "<p>Dynasty Headphone’s finishing touches are made to be touched, with matching aluminium details and woven fabric encasing the audio cable, charging cable and flight adapter.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_size": "medium",
            "button_style_secondary": false,
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker"
          }
        },
        "212b439a-6a88-4ae4-91aa-5847453b23ee": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image_position": "center center",
            "heading": "MUSIC AT YOUR FINGERTIPS",
            "description": "<p>More bass, more warmth, more you. Personalise your listening experience with the app. The equalizer and noise cancellation adjusters give you complete control over how you listen, with just a tap.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_size": "medium",
            "button_style_secondary": false,
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker"
          }
        },
        "fec6ec70-153a-4ad9-92cb-a79a5e023380": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image_position": "center center",
            "heading": "FIDELITY THAT FLEXES",
            "description": "<p>For the rare moments you'll take them off, Dynasty Headphone can be folded and placed into the custom hardcase, which is lined with a super soft textile finish. No matter how much you move, they'll be safe and sound.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_size": "medium",
            "button_style_secondary": false,
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker"
          }
        },
        "tab-collage-0-2": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image_position": "center center",
            "heading": "ALMOST-<em>UNREAL</em> COMFORT",
            "description": "<p>So comfortable, it's like you're not wearing them at all. Oval memory foam cushions, soft top grain lambskin and a superior fit invite you to play all day.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_size": "medium",
            "button_style_secondary": false,
            "enable_highlight": true,
            "highlight_style": "solid-color"
          }
        }
      },
